# after-hours (optional rule)

When the user runs **`/after-hours`**, **`/after-hours-loop`**, or **`/loop`** with after-hours / overnight AFK instructions, load and follow:

`.agents/skills/after-hours/SKILL.md`

Night Sources preset: `.cursor/after-hours-Sources.txt`

`/after-hours Nm` sets a **recurring** tick every N minutes; empty queue / `maxPrs` parks a tick and **keeps** the sentinel. Stop phrases (kill sentinel): `stop after-hours`, `stop loop`, `/after-hours stop`.
